{"tid":2192004,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人喺尿兜屙尿會屙唔出","createTime":"2020-09-06T23:41:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-05T06:56:30.000Z","uid":230821,"like":27,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"045077beacb2ddcad55b18c8c51f07c109f90d8b","tid":2192004,"uid":230821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T23:41:21.000Z","msg":"平時九成都會入廁格屙 但係廁格滿晒就焗住喺尿兜屙 冇人嘅話其實冇乜嘢 但係有人喺廁所就會有種無形嘅壓力 搞到我屙唔出<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲有少少尷尬嘅感覺 企喺尿兜面前10秒都未有得出 本身勁急都話好啲 如果淨係少少急就要等成世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 去廁所feel到有人喺隔離真係肚唔舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41a8927a3a36e8bcb868f42ba74b7a596715a5b5","tid":2192004,"uid":230821,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T23:43:21.000Z","msg":"閂埋門對住個馬桶就完全正常 好舒服咁搞掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc2ec90e2e830b55a75bfc85b6aacb3f0313ef19","tid":2192004,"uid":128102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T23:44:05.000Z","msg":"主要係尿兜驚彈到"},{"pid":"a86e9b1deb5bcbdc82b5b25dd5cb0df034a84279","tid":2192004,"uid":220185,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T23:51:43.000Z","msg":"我以為得我係甘 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我細個直頭廁格個門上下如果個罅隙太大都去唔到<br />\n總係覺得有人想偷望或者會衝入黎<br />\n黨鐵商場果隻密籠廁格去得好舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7312b3ea0034949505ac190a6170904258172ba5","tid":2192004,"uid":309443,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T23:52:27.000Z","msg":"我都有少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />可能怕醜驚比人睇賓周"},{"pid":"eab59962e484dc4cd7e3b06c8aa7a45c1333d73f","tid":2192004,"uid":230416,"like":0,"dislike":28,"score":-28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-